    dc:date "2017-03-15"^^xsd:string ;
    rdfs:comment "PMID:10830967 (ES): Whereas most glp-1(oz112 gf) animals and sterile and make tumorous germ lines at 25C (ref. 18) (Fig. 3h, upper row), most glp-1(oz112 gf); lag-3(RNAi) adults are either fertile or sterile with a Glp-1-like germ line composed solely of a few mature sperm (Fig. 3h), lower row). Thus, lag-3 is critical for glp-1 (GF) signalling."^^xsd:string ;
